Okay, now I can first say I really do not feel like logging into SuprBay forums and getting a new password for my old accounts, so if anyone is thinking I am some spammer with a rediculous comment, then think again. Anyone who has been with TPB for some years knows the name ReadyMan, and that is myself.

With that said I can say I have downloaded this torrent, so for those who are concerned with an honest answer from a former TPB Helper and still TPB VIP on the quality of this film, I feel I NEED to give my 2 cents.

This torrent needs to be renamed, it is not aXXo, aXXo is no longer ripping movies, therefor his name should not be re-placed in files that are not his. The tags state clearly that it is 'aXXo wannabe', this also needs to be removed. Since this is not aXXo's release himself, please remove any tag's referring to his name from this torrent, do not worry about the rername, it is quite okay to rename a torrent and label it as your own if it is not aXXo's. And I think that for the sake of popularity and 'customer support', a vast majority of the people would probably prefer if it did not have his name in it as well, since yet again, it is not his.

As far as the quality, it is a V-9 / A-9, and I will thank you for the great quality upload, because I am not one to bag on a free movie, especially one that is of good quality. It is tha aXXo name that is or may be creating a stir of madness on this torrent by some, and not the quality itself. It is a great torrent, and is worth the downlaod, I do recommentd it. Just do not expect it to be an aXXo original.

Sorry falconxx, it is not you, as you are only an uploader, not the ripper, I will fully acknowledge the quality, and assure all that it is no fake, or a dirty quality film, I am just going to say again, that you should consider renaming it, because once again it is not an aXXo release.

ThX for reading my comment, and please enjoy this torrent.

/ReadyMan
